data.description: Welcome home to this beauty located on a corner lot and oozing with curb appeal. The Villages @ Watervale is the perfect place to start a family! This home has been completely updated top to bottom and features a MASSIVE 2 car garage. Inside you will find the perfect touches after an extensive 6 month remodel. The kitchen features all new Stainless Steel Appliances and Granite Counters. You will notice that the interior of the home has been recently painted. All new light fixtures throughout. New vanities and plumbing fixtures in the bathrooms and kitchen and new carpet in the upstairs bedrooms. The main level features a clean look with all new luxury flooring. You will find a cozy living room with brick fireplace and even space for a private office. Don't miss out on this one today!
